    "The survey incorporated literature studies that deliberated on the variables influencing quantum communication.",
    "We also considered studies that did not explicitly discuss these variables (Niazi 2012 (Niazi, 2015)) as long as they offered pertinent lessons learned and experience reports related to quantum communication for smart cities.",
